Title: Le miserie del signor Travet
Writer: Vittorio Bersezio (play), Aldo De Benedetti (screenplay), Tullio Pinelli (screenplay), Carlo Musso (screenplay)
Actors: Carlo Campanini, Vera Carmi, Paola Veneroni, Pierluigi Veraldo
Plot: The ordinary life of the prudent employee Mr Travet accelerates as he and her wife meet his new chief.
